<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUH A THO CANG! CH145</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thlan chungah nang na um, Jesuh ka Khamhtu, Na thawh lai ni na ngan,
 Jesuh ka Bawi.

[C1]
   Thlan chungin Jesuh a tho, Lianhngannak in ral kha a tei hna, Mithi
   khua in thihnak teitu Bawi a tho, Ami pen awkah khan a zungzal a nung, A
   tho cang (A tho cang) A tho cang (A tho cang) Hal-le-lu-jah, a tho cang.

[V2]
 An hngah a thahnem lo, Jesuh ka Khamhtu, Thlan kha an phih fawn ko,
 Jesuh ka Bawi.

[C2]
   Thlan chungin Jesuh a tho, Lianhngannak in ral kha a tei hna, Mithi
   khua in thihnak teitu Bawi a tho, Ami pen awkah khan a zungzal a nung, A
   tho cang (A tho cang) A tho cang (A tho cang) Hal-le-lu-jah, a tho cang.

[V3]
 Thih nih an tlai kho lo, Jesuh ka Khamhtu, Thihnak kha na hrawh cang,
 Jesuh ka Bawi.

[C3]
   Thlan chungin Jesuh a tho, Lianhngannak in ral kha a tei hna, Mithi
   khua in thihnak teitu Bawi a tho, Ami pen awkah khan a zungzal a nung, A
   tho cang (A tho cang) A tho cang (A tho cang) Hal-le-lu-jah, a tho cang.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<hymn_number>145</hymn_number>
</song>